-----Hazy Maze-----
created by Killaplex
[Killaplex@hotmail.com]

Map Description

Ok basicly guy, Hazy maze is a huge maze filled with corridors and pits and other stuff, There is a number of zones and
enterances to the maze. there is a look out point called the "Sky tower" but this tower can only be accessed through one hallway!
This map is extremly large and i recommend playing with at least 6vs6!. Remember there is no objective, just to kill each other!
Enjoy!

Terrorists

You guys start at one side of the map your goal is to take out the counter-terrorist forces

Counter-Terrorists

You guys start on the other side of the map form the T's and your goal is to remove them from the game

Good luck!

TIP : Find your way to the Sky Tower, You can see most of the map from up the top!

Enjoy!
